g.title: j1531538379
g.text: Can target practice wait until tomorrow? I beg of you! I'm trying to sleep!

g.title: j435648436
g.text: uh... that message was meant for Quincy. sry... pls ignore this

g.title: j2522415278
g.text: Sounds like you're having a tough time.

g.title: j4107641501
g.text: no srsly. u can ignore this.

g.title: j2496137267
g.text: it's fiiine. this is a big mall. I can always find somewhere further from Quincy to nap

g.title: j2929497960
g.text: I'm sure he doesn't need to shoot things at *all* hours.

g.title: j3252990166
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j1553641191
g.text: nah it's for the best that I didn't reach him. he needs to let off steam. I get it.

g.title: j1867431639
g.text: I can say something to Arthur for you, if you want.

g.title: j787742124
g.text: As long as you're getting enough sleep, that's cool.

g.title: j925924790
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j1441171107
g.text: uh... I appreciate the thought, but if that was a good idea, I'd talk to Arthur myself :P

g.title: j1051418202
g.text: u wouldn't believe how cozy clothing stores can be

g.title: j3338477558
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j1950282544
g.text: Hey, I get it. I'd never tell Ordis how his jokes keep me up sometimes.

g.title: j2677410593
g.text: You should really look out for yourself more though.

g.title: j4266321569
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j2659629205
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j2849364138
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j491372234
g.text: You're always thinking about other people. I hope you don't forget about yourself.

g.title: j1229319119
g.text: Maybe I overstepped. It wasn't really my place to say that.

g.title: j4265180060
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j82215151
g.text: Yeah, he's the Cephalon intelligence that runs my spacecraft.

g.title: j465444073
g.text: No, he's the Cephalon intelligence that runs my spacecraft.

g.title: j2092485205
g.text: I just don't see looking out for others as separate from looking out for myself

g.title: j1611804500
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j3385724512
g.text: a Cephalon is like a... wut exactly?

g.title: j4048056826
g.text: Surely there are exceptions to that rule.

g.title: j4211395568
g.text: ew I feel like I need to shower after reading that

g.title: j986218862
g.text: They're people whose consciousness was uploaded to virtual space (usually by force.)

g.title: j3590910647
g.text: maybe we both need to sleep and reset, ya?

g.title: j377657138
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j3958257684
g.text: :) I'll have nightmares about that now

g.title: j2527641529
g.text: I respect others too much to accept bad behavior from them and respect myself too much to tolerate it

g.title: j3019714565
g.text: Damn. There I go sabotaging your sleep further.

g.title: j2655047361
g.text: What about people you don't respect?

g.title: j2724854221
g.text: Sounds like you're tolerating bad behavior from Quincy.

g.title: j4233192337
g.text: u and Quincy are quite the pair :P

g.title: j3445431960
g.text: why? wondering how I might feel about u? ;)

g.title: j3687160099
g.text: u mean target practice? I dunno. sounds like u have a low bar for bad behavior lol

g.title: j281583525
g.text: Maybe a little too futuristic to explain, honestly.

g.title: j3770818935
g.text: Your reaction to things that were normal to the Orokin is a good reality check for me.

g.title: j2927208683
g.text: I'm talking about him ignoring the needs of those around him.

g.title: j3145323029
g.text: well Ordis is lucky to have u

g.title: j3820523684
g.text: I respect u enough to let you find ur own answers to existential questions

g.title: j3303518544
g.text: sure, he shoots at odd hours, but I see ignoring it as a chance to do something kind for someone who truly deserves it

g.title: j1450365975
g.text: And I'm very lucky to have him.

g.title: j2474567118
g.text: anyway none of this cheery talk concerns Quincy :P

g.title: j2351104406
g.text: my respect is freely given, but it can be lost

g.title: j3951702267
g.text: All right, then. It's clear I can't convince you otherwise.

g.title: j3977960892
g.text: Your outlook does have a certain charm to it.

g.title: j3208775092
g.text: No, but it does concern you, so it interests me.

g.title: j3784169872
g.text: when that happens, I just stop caring and treat the person like anything else that holds no importance to me

g.title: j2992557203
g.text: time for me to go find a nice place to sleep
